Package: neuroim2
Type: Package
Title: Data Structures and IO for Neuroimaging Data with an Emphasis on FMRI Data
Version: 0.7.0
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Authors@R: c(
    person(c("Bradley", "R"), "Buchsbaum", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com"))
Maintainer: Bradley R Buchsbaum <brad.buchsbaum@gmail.com>
Description: A collection of data structures that represent
    volumetric brain imaging data. The focus is on basic data handling for 3D
    and 4D neuroimaging data. In addition, there are functions to read and write
     NIfTI-1 formats and some support for reading AFNI files.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
